skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: oshkosh airport
des:
This is a live stream which will let you listen into Oshkosh airport, the home of EAA Airventure. 
 This stream is simple. The audio feed comes from Broadcastify and covers the following. 
 125.9000 ATIS Arrival

121.7500 ATIS Depature

118.5000 Tower North (Runways 09 / 27)

126.6000 Tower South (Runways 18 / 36

119.0500 Clearance Delivery

132.3000 Ground Control

118.9000 VFR Departures From Runways 18-R / 36-L

126.6000 VFR Departures From Runway 18-L

128.7500 VFR Departures From Runways 9 / 27

120.7000 FISK Approach Control

122.9500 Basler Flight Service (FBO) / UNICOM

122.2500 Green Bay Flight Service Station

123.3000 Seaplane Base

123.7500 Ultralight / Rotocraft

123.9000 Warbird Ground Control

APPLETON INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT OUTAGAMIE COUNTY

127.1500 ATIS

119.6000 Tower

121.7000 Ground Control

124.2500 Clearance Delivery

126.3000 Green Bay Approach

122.9500 Platinum Flight Center / UNICOM

122.5500 Green Bay Flight Service Station (Airborne Only)

120.2000 Lake Michigan Crossing (North of Manitowoc Airport)

 Because this is a live stream and is as such communications, periods of long siolence will occur. The stream will begin with an ad and after this, the stream itself will begin playing. Just because you don't hear anything though, don't asume that the stream isn't working. It is. There isn't always activity. 
 With all of that said, I hope you will enjoy and know that this skill was made with love in Jesus Christ's mighty name!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
